.SH NAME
.\"
SAPHanaSR-tests-description_angi-DR-region \- Functional tests for SAPHanaSR-angi scale-up with DR HA for DR region.
.PP
.\"
.SH DESCRIPTION
.\"
Functional test are shipped for the scale-up with DR HA scenario. This tests
could be run out-of-the-box. The test cases are defined in dedicated files.
See manual page SAPHanaSR-tests-syntax(5) for syntax details.
Tests for SAPHanaSR-angi scale-up with DR HA for DR region scenario are listed
in SAPHanaSR-tests-angi-scale-up-DR-region(7).
.PP
Each test can be executed by running the command SAPHanaSR-testCluster with
appropriate parameters. See manual page SAPHanaSR-testCluster(8).
.PP
The tests are a sub-set of the SAPHanaSR-angi scale-up perf-opt progressive
tests. 
Main difference is that the DR region does not have an HANA primary. Instead of
the primary, one secondary (called third) is connected to the production region
and replicates to another secondary (called fourth).
So several CIB attributes are different. See manual page  SAPHanaSR_with_DR_HA(7).
.PP
